# Copy to .env.local and fill in. .env.local is gitignored.
#
# Sepolia JSON-RPC URL used for read-only contract queries from the browser
# (e.g. balance page).
#
# IMPORTANT: This URL ends up bundled into the client. Use a CORS-enabled
# provider (Alchemy, Infura, QuickNode). Public RPCs like rpc.sepolia.org
# are usually blocked by CORS in the browser.
#
# Treat this like any other key that is shipped to clients: rate-limit
# friendly, read-only by nature, but visible in DevTools.
VITE_SEPOLIA_RPC_URL=
